'''Greencliff Regional Spaceport''' was the smallest of the three [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] in [[Makrin City]], [[Shelkonwa]]. It was located in the [[City/Legends|city's]] northeast zone, along a series of cliffs that gave it its name.

